longBusinessSummary: Spectral Capital Corporation, a development stage company, focuses on the identification, acquisition, development, and financing of technology that has the potential to transform existing industries in the United States. The company provides telecommunications, data, and switching services; and international long distance reselling services, as well as routing solutions and direct bilateral connections with PTTs, Tier-1 carriers, and mobile operators. It focuses on acquiring and developing information technology; provides search engine technology for mobile devices that delivered personalized information to the user; technology application and services that enhances people to find, consume, analyze, share, and discuss financial news and topics, equities, commodities, and currencies on the web; and technology and financial data services that identifies for investors stocks that its software detects to be trending up in price at the moment to professional trading organizations. Spectral Capital Corporation was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Seattle, Washington.
